   11 root       171 ki31     0K    64K RUN    2  23.5H 31.88% {idle: cpu2}
   11 root       171 ki31     0K    64K RUN    1  19.9H 15.19% {idle: cpu1}
   11 root       171 ki31     0K    64K RUN    3  20.8H  9.18% {idle: cpu3}
